# Gap-Closure Supplement
## AI-Based ECD Decision Support Layer – Critical Review Response

This document closes five gaps identified in the critical review. It should be read alongside [ecd_system_architecture.md](file:///C:/Users/cnevi/.gemini/antigravity/brain/382a8dc0-c510-4fba-966d-20b69e5733cb/ecd_system_architecture.md) and [ecd_development_phases.md](file:///C:/Users/cnevi/.gemini/antigravity/brain/382a8dc0-c510-4fba-966d-20b69e5733cb/ecd_development_phases.md).

